# Kick.com Livestream Announcements Cog for Red Bot

I'll create a comprehensive cog that monitors Kick.com channels and posts beautiful embed announcements when streamers go live.

## Architecture Overview

Since Kick.com doesn't have an official public API with easy auth, we'll use their unofficial API endpoints (`https://kick.com/api/v2/channels/{username}`) to poll for livestream status.

